game_description: Become a Cube! Cube Runners Uses Unique Movement System Using Your Hands. Play Fun Gamemodes - There are a few different game modes to play Chat with friends - Join public rooms and chat with new people, maybe you'll even find a new friend! Other Things to do - You can customize yourself by changing your name, and colour and by also putting on some cosmetics!
